<br>
You know, you whisper something into one person's ear, they repeat what they heard, and so on down the line. At the end, it can be quite amusing.<br>
<br>
It also, not coincidentally, is my opinion of &quot;'eyewitness testimony&quot; in religious texts. <br>
<br>
